Usage: report_command_mode [-help] [-filter <string>] { -non_default | -user }

-help            # Prints out the command usage
-filter <string> # Specify the commands that will be reported by
                 # report_command_mode (string, optional)
-non_default     # Report all the *Mode options that do not match the default
                 # value (bool, optional)
-user            # Report all the *Mode options that have been manually set (to
                 # the default or other value) (bool, optional)